short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Fetch and display price history for Carsales listings on search results, saved items pages and individual listings.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
It is nice to know the price history of a car you may be looking it.
Want to know how long the car has been advertised?
Want to know how much the seller has dropped their price?
Want to know if a seller is negotiable?
